      • getReference

        public java.lang.String getReference​()
        Gets the reference.

        This attribute is used to store all the references from the different glyphs, meaning the 'compartment' for CompartmentGlyph, the 'species' for SpeciesGlyph, the 'reaction' for ReactionGlyph amd the 'reference' for GeneralGlyph.

        The optional reference attribute of type SIdRef that can be used to specify the id of the corresponding element in the model that is represented.
        If the reference attribute is used together with the metaidRef, they need to refer to the same object in the Model.

        Returns:
        the reference.
